The paper discusses the process of transforming raw data into curated data, which is a common theme in information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and databases (cs.DB). The use of APIs to extract and analyze data also falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
